Title: AU/NZ Office 2010 Launch Demos
Description: The AU/NZ Office 2010 Launch Demos are a collection of code samples that were used as part of the Office/SharePoint 2010 launch parties in Australia. These are great examples of what can be done in the 2010 release and can help get you started.
HomeWiki:
The AU/NZ Office 2010 Launch Demos are a collection of code samples that were used as part of the Office/SharePoint 2010 launch parties in Australia. These are great examples of what can be done in the 2010 release and can help get you started.

Be sure to check out the main launch website at http://www.aunz2010launch.net as well!
